  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bounce and break everything as you roll downhill in this beautiful game!</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play normally for a relaxed experience or push your skills to the limit in hard mode. Destroy every object while maintaining momentum, exploding, bouncing, using power-ups, and avoiding all kinds of deadly obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience simple yet finely-tuned gameplay with numerous levels, secrets, and rewards to customize your hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock over 100 items to customize your hero with different expressions, clothes, costumes, and accessories.<br></li><li>Learn how different objects react to your actions!<br></li><li>Play through 60 amazing levels.<br></li><li>Discover incredible power-ups!<br></li><li>Choose between two difficulty modes: Normal and Hard.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Bounce and break everything as you roll downhill in this beautiful game!</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/d3621803ae166b5b4a54f5db8bd2ff07.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play normally for a relaxed experience or push your skills to the limit in hard mode. Destroy every object while maintaining momentum, exploding, bouncing, using power-ups, and avoiding all kinds of deadly obstacles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/cf6c0c7249b0dda38a1a2ec28477902f.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience simple yet finely-tuned gameplay with numerous levels, secrets, and rewards to customize your hero.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.poster.avif?t=1732695487\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.webm?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787720/extras/7f7a5d1c200dbf5510198a01de4852f4.mp4?t=1732695487\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unlock over 100 items to customize your hero with different expressions, clothes, costumes, and accessories.<br></li><li>Learn how different objects react to your actions!<br></li><li>Play through 60 amazing levels.<br></li><li>Discover incredible power-ups!<br></li><li>Choose between two difficulty modes: Normal and Hard.</li></ul>",
